dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_Addresses_2013.gdb. [This feature class represents a comprehensive, spatially referenced collection of rural addresses as recognized by Waupaca County. This layer represents the location/address of primary structures (generally residential housing) throughout the County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. For complete metadata documentation and most current online dataset download, please visit http://data-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/ [This file is rarely (if ever) fully representative of a dynamically changing landscape, the best that can be expected is data relative to a specific point in time.]
